posts/949027942142697?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n#中學生銀髮族跨代connect<br />\n#不要催淚煙不要二噁英<br />\n#查警暴"},{"pid":"1901096caee8d570b9c564424e1db08d180f93fc","tid":1762830,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2328a72837108642e92c7fde06e335dd527c5d88","tid":1762830,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ba59b90ded46bd562c8b85d9b51b914153289d9","tid":1762830,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4f8f850759cd1ec987a65834433253f9cd9bd06e","tid":1762830,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:11:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"62479c9a390bf44dc0bacb8e80fa53960c5784d9","tid":1762830,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"知道大家都好攰 但我們必須堅持<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"ecbe8d131527d84f93cb0a801e7364956d8e320b","tid":1762830,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru